..TEXT:
These three stars are the ^Alphae~ of Euridanus,
of the Ship, and of the Golden Fish; allegorically, if any
allegory be wanted, the three Theological Virtues, Faith, Hope,
and Charity.  The four morning stars, the Cardinal Virtues of
active life, are already set; these announce the evening and the
life contemplative.
